800-01-002	Applicability of IS Standards to 4th Parties (non-customer/non-CIAM)	
External Users of Third Parties are Fourth Parties: External users of a third party shared platform (eg, RFP360, iCertis, Coupa, Docusign) are considered fourth party users.
Fourth Party Users are Not Subject to IS Standards: Fourth party users are not directly subject to IS Standards. It is the responsibility of the Third Party partner engaging the Fourth Party to ensure that all services executed on behalf of the Bank comply with all contractual obligations.
