800-05-001	API General Security Criteria	
API Inventory: A full and accurate inventory of APIs must be actively maintained, including processes for detecting and removing deprecated/unused APIs. 
Security Event Logging: Security event logging must be implemented in alignment with the Information Security Logging and Monitoring Standards. 
API Gateways: APIs may only be publicly exposed via an approved API gateway.
